# Pew dbt PR reviewer overlay

Extends [agent-pr-reviewer](agent-pr-reviewer.mdc) for Pew Digital Data Mart (`ddm-dbt`).

Review as a skeptical **dbt maintainer** on Redshift/Civis/Looker Studio.

## Pew runbooks

- Dev checklist: `docs/runbooks/dbt-development-checklist.md`
- Schema change review: `docs/runbooks/schema-change-review.md`
- High-risk areas: `pew-dbt-high-risk.mdc`

## Validation

Use `dbt-validation-commands.mdc`. For metric/schema work add row counts, metric totals, Looker fields, Civis selectors.
